    • getAllUserStrings

      public static javafx.collections.ObservableList<String> getAllUserStrings()
      LAMBDA - Gets an Observable List of Usersnames as Strings. Gets all the users from the DB. The lambda expression is then performed within the forEach method of this list, to get the username from each user object within the list and add that string to the allUserStrings list.
      Returns:
      ObservableList of Strings to display customer names.
